</seg></rs>«, eine Studie von <rs type="pers" ana="n_22949" ref="#fk__p_47149"><seg type="spc">Joseph Schöffel</seg></rs><lb/>
(II.)</contItem> — <contItem contItemID="ci_0711" href="FK-04-117_n0018.xml" firstParParID="pr26230"><seg type="insult">Der freigesprochene Mörder.</seg></contItem> —<lb/>
<contItem contItemID="ci_0712" href="FK-04-117_n0021.xml" targetType="div" targetID="pr26239" firstParParID="pr26240"><seg type="insult"><foreign xml:lang="fr"><rs type="pers" ana="n_22950" ref="#fk__p_42655">Zola</rs> est mort, vive <rs type="pers" ana="n_22951" ref="#fk__p_38056">Dreyfus</rs>!</foreign></seg></contItem> — <contItem contItemID="ci_0713" href="FK-04-117_n0023.xml" firstParParID="pr26245"><seg type="insult">Ein Austausch<lb/>
 von Kräften.</seg></contItem> — <contItem contItemID="ci_0714" href="FK-04-117_n0025.xml" targetType="div" targetID="pr26249" firstParParID="pr26250">Das Scharlach-Heilserum<lb/>
