<B><HR type="doubleInline" emDashNum="4"/> <rs type="pers" ana="n_22961" ref="#fk__p_47565">Karl Kraus</rs> <HR type="doubleInline" emDashNum="4"/></B><lb/>
</p>
            <p ana="pr26514">
(Sonderabdruck).<lb/>
</p>
